Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.95,0:01:45.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.12,0:01:47.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,终于找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.80,0:01:50.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等着我 萤
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.13,0:01:52.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就把白浪给带回去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.83,0:02:08.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白浪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.91,0:02:10.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我到处找你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.68,0:02:12.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就是白浪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.14,0:02:14.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中计了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.34,0:02:19.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梦 幻 泡 影
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.34,0:02:30.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然什么都没说就走了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.33,0:02:32.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诗形大人 我还…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.46,0:02:42.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,参见役之行者的孙女萤小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.82,0:02:44.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁 是谁…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.31,0:02:48.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在下白浪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.90,0:02:50.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白浪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.47,0:02:51.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,解
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.96,0:02:56.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,终于见到你了 萤小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.71,0:02:58.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.03,0:03:06.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个纹章仅授予能够传承禁术的人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.08,0:03:09.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道真是白浪大人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.25,0:03:12.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你如此吃惊也可以理解
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.18,0:03:15.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实我是从鸣人那听说了事情的缘由
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.22,0:03:17.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.08,0:03:20.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果真是白浪大人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.94,0:03:22.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.00,0:03:24.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得好好谢谢他
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.75,0:03:28.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他已经不在这里了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.87,0:03:32.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说了句“之后就拜托你了” 便离开了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.29,0:03:37.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这样啊 鸣人…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.91,0:03:42.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听鸣人说 你想复兴家族
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.27,0:03:44.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.69,0:03:49.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是真心的话 能够听一下我的建议吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.61,0:03:52.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白浪大人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.38,0:03:59.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遁兵卫还健在吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.41,0:04:03.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,据说他想通过分离之术埋葬禁术
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.09,0:04:05.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你认识遁兵卫吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.09,0:04:08.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们一起修行过
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.58,0:04:12.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我不同意遁兵卫的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.51,0:04:13.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.08,0:04:20.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我父波涛曾受役之行者大人之命保护禁术
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.32,0:04:26.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,父亲是一直守护禁术和土蜘蛛一族荣耀的英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.53,0:04:32.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直到被盯上禁术的人杀死之前
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.19,0:04:36.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以父亲的死为契机
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.15,0:04:40.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,役之行者大人将禁术转移到了葛城山要塞
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.86,0:04:42.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后让我从村中逃走
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.50,0:04:45.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我曾发过誓
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.31,0:04:50.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总有一日 会为土蜘蛛一族重返
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.08,0:04:52.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白浪大人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.24,0:04:54.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,萤小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.65,0:04:58.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,父亲被杀 我不得不逃出村子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.14,0:05:03.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是因为我们父子是掌握禁术的唯一幸存者
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.26,0:05:06.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他也有着同样的烦恼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.32,0:05:10.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 我变强了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.59,0:05:12.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和萤小姐合力的话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.06,0:05:14.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定能复活禁术
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.76,0:05:17.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而不用埋葬它
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.37,0:05:21.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,复兴土蜘蛛一族也是我的夙愿
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.60,0:05:26.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们一起实现父亲和役之行者的梦想吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.01,0:05:30.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.08,0:05:32.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,翻过这座山
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.76,0:05:34.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是我的藏身之处
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.31,0:05:36.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,萤小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.97,0:05:42.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.16,0:05:45.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,萤不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.29,0:05:48.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这要塞的周边已经大致搜查过了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.19,0:05:54.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人找到白浪的事明明已经告诉她了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.92,0:05:58.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟着诗形出去了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.45,0:05:59.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.34,0:06:01.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.31,0:06:03.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先中止仪式的准备
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.35,0:06:05.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,优先搜索萤
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.24,0:06:07.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佐井
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.06,0:06:09.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能多放出一些搜索用的老鼠吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.37,0:06:11.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.54,0:06:14.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,忍法.超兽伪画
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.99,0:06:18.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,写给遁兵卫吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.81,0:06:22.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定要联系一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.04,0:06:26.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至少也要跟诗形大人说一声
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.95,0:06:34.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.75,0:06:37.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧 白浪大人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.29,0:06:42.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伤脑筋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.20,0:06:45.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.79,0:06:48.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.40,0:06:51.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁让你肆意妄为了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.95,0:06:58.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本以为早就割舍了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.07,0:07:01.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么此刻我仍对师父的事…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.10,0:07:04.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.05,0:07:07.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是查克拉操纵的文字
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.06,0:07:22.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,信鸽
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.74,0:07:27.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,萤发来的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.30,0:07:29.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,致诗形大人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.48,0:07:35.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和白浪大人同以复兴土蜘蛛一族为目标
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.41,0:07:38.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之前的种种非常感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.00,0:07:41.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.93,0:07:43.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弟子萤 敬上
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.64,0:07:46.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,萤
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.60,0:07:51.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到白浪了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.07,0:07:55.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这下我也解放了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.64,0:08:06.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们是什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.30,0:08:07.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道白浪被…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.64,0:08:11.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是个不折不扣的傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.30,0:08:14.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然还在担心白浪老大呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.95,0:08:17.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让你和禁术丫头见面的话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.60,0:08:20.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的计划就泡汤了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.40,0:08:22.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少说废话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.56,0:08:25.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别担心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.29,0:08:27.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个结界是老大特制的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.41,0:08:30.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是能夺取对方查克拉的经典之作啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.64,0:08:33.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这结界中还能反抗的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.63,0:08:34.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什…什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.88,0:08:36.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可…可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.05,0:08:37.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,动手
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.92,0:08:47.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙 有一手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.10,0:08:49.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要慌
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.33,0:08:51.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,按照老大的作战 使用下一个术
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.59,0:08:54.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多重.梦幻泡影
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.59,0:09:03.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样你就解不开了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.39,0:09:05.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.47,0:09:11.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种东西没什么了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.51,0:09:12.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.24,0:09:26.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到被剥夺了这么多查克拉竟然还能动
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.36,0:09:28.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在是佩服他的时候吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.44,0:09:30.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点动手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.75,0:09:34.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.41,0:09:41.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.54,0:09:47.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才的事 我听到了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.48,0:09:50.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到匪首竟然是白浪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.32,0:09:54.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们把萤带到哪里去了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.93,0:10:01.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙是谁…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.64,0:10:03.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不妙啊 赤星
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.51,0:10:06.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老大应该到村子了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.65,0:10:07.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们也撤
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.17,0:10:19.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.41,0:10:21.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,土蜘蛛一族的村子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.77,0:10:24.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,醒了吗 萤小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.13,0:10:27.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白浪大人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.51,0:10:32.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位 出来吧 萤小姐回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.03,0:10:37.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些人…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.29,0:10:40.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,村里的人这是怎么了…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.65,0:10:41.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.83,0:10:45.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是略施小术让他们听话一些罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.05,0:10:47.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没办法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.85,0:10:51.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这都是为了得到禁术这个宝贝啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.24,0:10:55.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白浪大人 你骗了我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.35,0:10:57.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没骗你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.08,0:10:59.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才是我的真心话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.06,0:11:01.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,需要补充的是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.00,0:11:05.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀了保护禁术的老爸的人正是我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.16,0:11:12.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我为了抢走禁术而杀了老爸 萤小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.01,0:11:16.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没用的 没用的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.79,0:11:19.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你已经在我的控制中了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.45,0:11:22.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,禁术
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.97,0:11:26.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,终于得到禁术了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.82,0:11:33.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是枯枝吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.34,0:11:36.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,与其这么没效率地搜索
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.18,0:11:39.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还不如用多重影分身来得更快
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.83,0:11:44.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是想毁掉萤被带走的重要线索吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.79,0:11:47.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能有如此体重的人…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.00,0:11:51.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错 是带着一个人奔跑时留下的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.19,0:11:53.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这边
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.13,0:11:55.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.65,0:12:00.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从留下的痕迹中搜索是忍者最基本的常识
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.53,0:12:01.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也和萤一样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.00,0:12:06.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,张口闭口师傅 看来并没有好好修行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.33,0:12:08.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有的事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.91,0:12:15.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.12,0:12:18.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是因为执着于师父这种无聊的事才会变成这样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.79,0:12:21.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.11,0:12:24.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可不无聊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.69,0:12:28.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我从好色仙人那里学到了很多东西
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.04,0:12:32.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,体术和忍术就不说了 还有非常厉害的术
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.19,0:12:35.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但他并不只是严格要求我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.08,0:12:40.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作为忍者而言 最重要的是不放弃的毅力
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.81,0:12:48.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可是从师父那里得到了最重要的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.17,0:12:49.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可能无聊呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.26,0:12:52.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也有师父吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.77,0:12:56.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和师父一起的回忆…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.49,0:13:01.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,任务完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.99,0:13:05.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所谓忍者 就要迅速完成任务
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.67,0:13:07.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吧 师父
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.81,0:13:09.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这个笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.78,0:13:14.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的任务是追踪被夺走的卷轴
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.64,0:13:17.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁让你抢回来的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.47,0:13:19.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最重要的可是生命啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.58,0:13:21.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要糟蹋生命
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.92,0:13:26.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,临阵脱逃不配做忍者
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.58,0:13:30.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是不可为而为之也不能算是忍者
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.75,0:13:33.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.18,0:13:38.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.84,0:13:41.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,师父
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.90,0:13:45.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我本以为自己对师父很重要
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.55,0:13:47.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.88,0:13:55.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那股力量 是超越你器量的东西…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.53,0:13:58.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住…住手…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.50,0:14:06.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,重要的并不是我 而是我体内的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.08,0:14:13.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是把我看成了容器而已
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.64,0:14:18.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 剑所言属实的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.11,0:14:22.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.05,0:14:34.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么啊 这不是土蜘蛛一族的村子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.12,0:14:35.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.87,0:14:39.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是痕迹一直延续到了这个村子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.22,0:14:40.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是发生过什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.25,0:14:44.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,萤在这个村子遭到了贼匪们的袭击
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.06,0:14:46.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,此外…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.72,0:14:52.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,村里的人并不欢迎萤
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.41,0:14:57.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这里 禁术是令人忌讳的存在 这很好理解
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.20,0:15:02.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再加上萤在此被袭击
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.59,0:15:07.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能贼匪和村民相互勾结 又或许是村民视而不见
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.90,0:15:12.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之 这个村子就像贼匪们的据点一样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.34,0:15:18.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,此外 留下的脚印也相当不自然
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.38,0:15:22.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是得到禁术和萤之后大意了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.13,0:15:26.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是打算引我们上钩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.33,0:15:27.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是陷阱吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.01,0:15:29.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就不清楚了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.46,0:15:30.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.37,0:15:32.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目前为止 追踪过于顺利
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.74,0:15:35.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,顺利的追踪反而值得怀疑 我从师父那…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.21,0:15:38.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总而言之要小心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.71,0:15:44.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来你也从师父那学到不少东西嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.36,0:15:49.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,救回萤之后 也分享一些给她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.05,0:15:52.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.82,0:16:02.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的是这里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.45,0:16:05.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是这么认为的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.82,0:16:20.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.53,0:16:23.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作为谢礼 这个给你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.61,0:16:32.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.71,0:16:35.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出现了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.04,0:16:43.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道他们要和贼匪联手对付我们吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.16,0:16:45.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.87,0:16:47.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来不太对劲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.26,0:16:49.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家似乎被操纵了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.20,0:16:50.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.71,0:16:55.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如此卑鄙的手段
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.58,0:16:57.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.69,0:17:12.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.73,0:17:24.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来没法不伤害村民继续前进了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.19,0:17:28.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 怎么办才好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.65,0:17:34.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才的气势哪儿去了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.21,0:17:36.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真狼狈啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.22,0:17:37.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.53,0:17:39.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是他们把村民给…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.48,0:17:42.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,动手 别给他们喘息的机会
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.83,0:17:51.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.31,0:18:02.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佐井
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.11,0:18:11.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大和队长
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.10,0:18:13.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.12,0:18:15.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小樱
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.23,0:18:18.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.87,0:18:25.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,单独行动也该适可而止了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.15,0:18:27.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 你们为什么会在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.69,0:18:31.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们在寻找从葛城山失踪的萤
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.31,0:18:33.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佐井很努力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.02,0:18:36.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可不是体力劳动型
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.33,0:18:39.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然耗费了这么多查克拉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.57,0:18:41.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给 兵粮丸
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.84,0:18:43.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等会再给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.75,0:18:45.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.39,0:18:48.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说这种话 万一发生什么事怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.75,0:18:52.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我特制的兵粮丸 一定要恢复精神啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.13,0:18:55.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个非常难吃吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.79,0:18:58.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少磨磨蹭蹭了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.92,0:19:03.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,电光石火
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.68,0:19:12.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.68,0:19:20.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到此为止了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.46,0:19:23.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能让你们妨碍老大的仪式
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.36,0:19:34.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火缚之术
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.04,0:19:44.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,耗费了那么多时间辛苦去做准备也算是得到回报了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.98,0:19:49.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从禁术中被解放 你也应该相当激动吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.30,0:19:54.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.16,0:19:56.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佐井 小樱
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.35,0:20:04.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大和队长
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.16,0:20:08.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,木遁之术
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.02,0:20:21.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大和队长
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.35,0:20:23.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们俩先走
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.05,0:20:27.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.29,0:20:29.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里交给我们 鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.68,0:20:31.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人 快走
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.54,0:20:33.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去救萤
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.87,0:20:37.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位 拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.87,0:20:59.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就来救你 萤
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.55,0:22:38.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.30,0:22:40.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么说前面的查克拉在不断聚集
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.30,0:22:43.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自然界的查克拉正朝着同一方向流去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.26,0:22:44.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仿佛被某处吸收了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.86,0:22:46.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,萤恐怕就在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.46,0:22:47.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.61,0:22:51.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白浪那家伙到底想干吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.45,0:22:53.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事态刻不容缓
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.19,0:22:55.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有动嘴的时间不如加快脚步
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.19,0:22:58.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下集火影忍者疾风传
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.27,0:22:59.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,禁术发动
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.29,0:23:02.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,萤 我们这就到了
